Instructions for compiling Cli Calc from source code

Requirements (tested on):
- libgmp 3 or newer
- g++ 4.4.3 or newer
- make 3.8 or newer

For Debian:
- sudo apt-get install build-essential libgmp3-dev make

Steps:
- make
- make install
(might require administrator priveleges)

Unistall:
- make uninstall
(might require administrator priveleges)
